	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. (names entire); Polyb. 1.20.4; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; see Degrassi, 42f., 115, 432f. Both Consuls campaigned in Sicily (Polyb. 1.20.3-7; cf. Diod. 23.9; Frontin. Str. 3.16.3; Zon. 8.10). On Valerius, see Münzer, Gent. Val. 38, no. 15; on Otacilius, Lübker no. 2." .
